    set {_rod} to diamond sword named "&2ğŸ—¡&ağŸ—¡&fğŸ—¡ &a&lTOKEN EXTRACTOR &fğŸ—¡&ağŸ—¡&2ğŸ—¡" with lore ("&8Slaying Tool", "", " &fâ†’ &aKill the chickens at /spawn!", "", "&7á´‹ÉªÊŸÊŸ á´›Êœá´sá´‡ á´„ÊœÉªá´„á´‹á´‡É´s!") with all flags hidden
    enchant {_rod} with efficiency 5
